query:
ALTER TABLE initiatives 
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS impactBenefitType ENUM('patient-safety', 'patient-outcomes', 'staff-efficiency', 'cost-reduction', 'experience'),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS impactFinancialReturn ENUM('high', 'some', 'minimal'),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS impactScore INT,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS feasibilityComplexity ENUM('simple', 'moderate', 'complex'),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS feasibilityTimeline ENUM('quick', 'standard', 'long'),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS feasibilityDependencies ENUM('ready', 'minor', 'major'),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS feasibilityScore INT;
